    "description": "《烟之书》是一款结合和卡组构建和自走棋设计的roguelike游戏，由来自中国的独立游戏团队<strong>离经</strong>创作。<br><br>你正在酒吧喝酒，忽然对面坐过来一位美丽的女子，她神秘一笑，递过来一本书，告诉你只要翻到这本书的最后一页，她就答应你一个要求。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色：</h2><strong>极致的卡组构建</strong><br>每次你将选择至少3组套牌开始游戏，每组套牌间都有等待你发掘的搭配机制，让你在游戏过程中可以构建产生尽可能巨大能量的套牌。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042570/extras/edee0d8578dbf6592a233ea3e3ce9d76.poster.avif?t=1733484073\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042570/extras/edee0d8578dbf6592a233ea3e3ce9d76.webm?t=1733484073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042570/extras/edee0d8578dbf6592a233ea3e3ce9d76.mp4?t=1733484073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>自走棋？</strong><br>只需要点下出牌按钮，便可享受经过自己精心配置后的卡牌间的联动效果。每回合你将有机会调整卡牌的顺序，或将卡牌保留在手中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042570/extras/dc315999e5756fb146513c5f403abc8c.poster.avif?t=1733484073\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042570/extras/dc315999e5756fb146513c5f403abc8c.webm?t=1733484073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042570/extras/dc315999e5756fb146513c5f403abc8c.mp4?t=1733484073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>花语印章</strong><br>想要临时提升某张卡牌的效果？想要永久增强某张卡牌的能力？想要获得更高的分数？花语印章将满足你的期望。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042570/extras/e8b66e251a587013d235fbc51da58eaf.poster.avif?t=1733484073\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042570/extras/e8b66e251a587013d235fbc51da58eaf.webm?t=1733484073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042570/extras/e8b66e251a587013d235fbc51da58eaf.mp4?t=1733484073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>神秘图案</strong><br>你将有机会获取强大的迷雾卡牌，或许这些卡牌才是你构建牌组的真正核心。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042570/extras/59e6d5729e1b4909b4ad060c1e5cebc4.poster.avif?t=1733484073\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042570/extras/59e6d5729e1b4909b4ad060c1e5cebc4.webm?t=1733484073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042570/extras/59e6d5729e1b4909b4ad060c1e5cebc4.mp4?t=1733484073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>独特符号</strong><br>每种符号都将增强你的套牌能量，使你可以更迅猛地探寻无尽的迷雾之书。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042570/extras/7b3450d3561feda8a891a90cd5922c83.poster.avif?t=1733484073\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042570/extras/7b3450d3561feda8a891a90cd5922c83.webm?t=1733484073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042570/extras/7b3450d3561feda8a891a90cd5922c83.mp4?t=1733484073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>挑战书签</strong><br>每个章节你都可以选择一枚书签，以此来换取更为需要的探寻能力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042570/extras/e24300b66803b3e02850e61456b46685.poster.avif?t=1733484073\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042570/extras/e24300b66803b3e02850e61456b46685.webm?t=1733484073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042570/extras/e24300b66803b3e02850e61456b46685.mp4?t=1733484073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
